Package: parallelRemake
Title: "Parallelize Remake-Style Workflows with Makefiles"
Version: 0.0.0
Date: 2016-09-17
Authors@R: person("Landau", "William", email = "will.landau@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Parallelize a workflow that uses remake (Rich FitzJohn, https://richfitz.github.io/)
    by generating a Makefile, which can distribute the work over multiple parallel processes with 
    system("make -j").
License: GPL (>= 3)
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.0)
Imports:
    crayon,
    remake,
    storr,
    stringr,
    yaml
Remotes: richfitz/remake
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Suggests: testthat
